  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ allows businesses to personalize their environment by replacing default logos with their own. This is a great way to establish your brand and promote your business. Admin users can add a logo to the RepairQ login screen, Navigation bar, Qsite, receipts/invoices, and more.</p><p>This article will demonstrate how to update our logo for the RepairQ login screen, the RepairQ Navigation Bar, and Qsite. For instructions on how to add your logo to other areas, check out the following articles:</p><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933279270/Add+Your+Logo+to+Receipts+and+Invoices\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933279270\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Add Your Logo to Receipts and Invoices</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937047567/Qpop+Companion+Resources+with+Video\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937047567\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Introduction to Qpop Companion - Start Here!</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523327/Qsite+Resources\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523327\" data-linked-resource-version=\"14\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qsite\u2122 Resources</a></p></li></ul><h3 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-LogoImageResolutionSuggestions\">Logo Image Resolution Suggestions</h3><ul><li><p>Login Page: 270 width x 90 height or larger</p></li><li><p>Navigation Bar: 125 width x 25 height</p></li><li><p>Qsite Customer Portal: 270 width x 90 height or larger</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175251.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-ExamplesofLogosThatCanbeReplacedinRepairQ\">Examples of Logos That Can be Replaced in RepairQ</h2><h3 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-LoginScreen\">Login Screen</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175257.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-NavigationBar\">Navigation Bar</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175304.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-QsiteTicketStatus\">Qsite Ticket Status</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175310.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-AddYourLogototheBrandingImageLibrary\">Add Your Logo to the Branding Image Library</h2><p /><p>1. From the Navigation Bar, go to <strong>Settings</strong> \u2192  <strong>Company Settings</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" width=\"776\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175317.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. On the Settings Overview page, click  <strong>Miscellaneous</strong> on the left-side settings column to expand the category, then select <strong>Branding Image Library</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175325.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>3. The Logos page will list your library of images. To add a logo, click the <strong>Add</strong> <strong>button</strong> on the right side of the page.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175332.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>4. An Add Image pop-up will appear. If the image is online, you can paste the URL into the text box and click <strong>Add from URL</strong>. If the image is on your computer, you can drag and drop your image into the Image Upload Box or click Browse to locate the image file.</p><p><strong>Note:\u00a0</strong>Before uploading, include the destination in your file name for easier identification when selecting an image. Example: &quot;RepairbrosNavbar&quot; or &quot;RepairbrosLogin&quot;.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175340.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>5. Once your images have been uploaded, they will be visible in your Branding Image Library. If you would like to delete any images, click the red X button on the image.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175346.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"AddingYourCompanyLogotoRepairQ-ReplacingDefaultLogoImages\">Replacing Default Logo Images</h2><p /><p>1. Navigate back to <strong>Settings</strong> \u2192 <strong>Company Settings</strong>. On the Settings Overview page, click  <strong>Miscellaneous</strong> on the left-side settings column to expand the category, then select <strong>Branding</strong>.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175353.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p>2. On the Logos page, use the dropdown selections to replace the current logos with your uploads. The image previews will change to show your image within the logo area. When you are satisfied with your selection(s), click <strong>Update</strong>.</p><p>Your logos will be updated. If you need to make any adjustments, follow the above steps to add/replace images and update your changes.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image confluence-content-image-border image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936326777/image-20230607-175359.png?api=v2\"></span><p /><p /><p>START 1.20.X</p>",
